rComments: Tons of reading, but it's all super interesting and you can choose what to focus on. Interesting lectures, some small group discussions/in-class projects. Way better than I expected for a non-Indigenous prof teaching this course. For FEM2503 she did an OK job of making methodology interesting, there were boring group projects.

Amazing prof!! Very clear criteria and really cares that you succeed. Awesome feedback and super easy to approach. The course work is fairly simple and final is a take home. I would take any class with this prof again she's great.
Cours pas intéressant. Manque de regard autochtone et trop général. prof. pas passionné pas le savoir autochtone.
I really enjoyed this class. She's passionate when she teaches and it creates a great environment. I learned a lot and I would recommend this class.
She does everything she can to make you fail the class. Good luck having an A in this class.
